{"tid":689630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(平反)吳三桂唔係漢奸，因為滿洲族都係中華民族一分子","createTime":"2018-06-04T08:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:24:40.000Z","uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"486b3863f4cad06e8ec111e1b2eafa49f5f23bc5","tid":689630,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:20:34.000Z","msg":"A:吳三桂放清兵入關,消滅了漢族的大好江山,把他稱為漢奸,真是實至名歸呢!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nB:清朝的滿洲族現在已是中華民族的一分子.換言之,吳三桂放清兵入關只不過想讓兄弟回家<br />\n<br />\n而不屬於兄弟之戰,把吳三桂視為漢奸當然不恰當阿<br />\n<br />\n大家話係唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9680679ec7259e26467ba79721a1e8f03bbb382c","tid":689630,"uid":126044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">漢</span></span></strong>奸<br />\n<br />\n樓豬on9"}]}